1-03-26T17:49:26.000Z","msg":"你當我係AI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T17:51:02.000Z","msg":"扮緊幽默冇唔禮貌既意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2344149f470b95dfd44da96d951da26f05064722","tid":2463486,"uid":32672,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"2ac1ac9ac5bafa80cc3d25ca6357b415ce9f6323","tid":2463486,"uid":305799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6023754026e71c46b865453dbb72b4e279bba28f","tid":2463486,"uid":32672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb86338b36a48b97a40a36086a2fd14e666f19d8","tid":2463486,"uid":305799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T17:45:01.000Z","msg":"冇文都開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T17:49:26.000Z","msg":"你當我係AI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T17:51:02.000Z","msg":"扮緊幽默冇唔禮貌既意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T17:54:38.000Z","msg":"好啦，當我燥咗，送返個額外出文畀大家！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nChapter 10 【掙扎】<br />\n<br />\n有人說熱戀期只能維持三個月，但我們戀愛已經快要五個月，紀念日將至，我們手牽手，進入對方的人生，再慢慢在對方的日常留下足跡，由春回大地的回南天，一直熱戀到炎夏。<br />\n<br />\n「五個月快樂啦陳生。」<br />\n<br />\n家瑜在床邊擁著我說了這句話，我們不知不覺便戀愛了五個月，而這段關係在悄悄萌芽了五個月，倘若我們的關係就像一位孩子的話，家瑜應該見肚了。<br />\n<br />\n我到底在想甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n五個月紀念日那天剛好是周六，於是家瑜決定周五到我家過夜，周六那晚我訂了一間海景酒店的套房，周五晚上剛好撘正十二點，我們正式戀愛了五個月。<br />\n<br />\n五個月紀念日的周六，我為家瑜安排了行程，家瑜也悉心打扮了，穿起一條較為性感的連身裙，首先我送了一隻Apple Watch給她，她跟我說今晚有驚喜禮物；<br />\n<br />\n我們睡得自然起床，再慢慢梳洗出門，首先請她吃一頓酒店的下午茶，讓她可以充當港女打卡，她也很快地更新了兩則限時動態，一張是Apple Watch的照片，另一張這頓酒店的下午茶，兩張照片也附加上一個hashtag；<br />\n<br />\n#五個月快樂<br />\n#我好幸福<br />\n<br />\n那一刻，我也恨不得可以把我們的幸福在instagram公開，可惜.....<br />\n<br />\n然後晚餐則滿足她的童心......吃了一餐KFC，我問她為甚麼想吃KFC，她跟我說因為怕肥，而我繼續問為甚麼今晚可以吃？<br />\n<br />\n她在我耳邊說了一句：<br />\n<br />\n「今晚會做好劇烈嘅運動補返。」<br />\n<br />\n這一句話，簡直令我急不及待！但是我們就是儀式感很重的一對，總覺得晚飯過後，需要淺酌一杯，慶祝我們經過五個月的考驗依然甜蜜依然。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n待續！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f13a3d40a0a48727bf40c857224bfaf1bf47d2","tid":2463486,"uid":147086,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"2344149f470b95dfd44da96d951da26f05064722","tid":2463486,"uid":32672,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"2ac1ac9ac5bafa80cc3d25ca6357b415ce9f6323","tid":2463486,"uid":305799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6023754026e71c46b865453dbb72b4e279bba28f","tid":2463486,"uid":32672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T17:49:26.000Z","msg":"你當我係AI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\